  "texts": [
    "a = | |M μ a ⟩ ⟨M μ a | | and Πν b = | | M ν b * ⟩ ⟨M ν b * | |, where | |M μ a ⟩ = 1 √d ∑ d-1 m=0 ω am+μm 2 d",
    "|m⟩ on the basis of each implemented circuit, and ω d = exp(2πi/d) is the dth root of unity.",
